Quickstrike:




Quickstrike made his way through the forest, left behind by the 
others, as far as he was concerned. His stomach was hurting again, 
now that his mind off the fight. He could find something to eat in 
the forest while on his way back to the bunker.

He didn't quite understand while the others retreated while he 
fought, and wanted a bigger fight while he was at it. It was just a 
complaint he could tell to them. He was after all high ranked.
